<div>two things:</div><div>1. Too many mpi processes on one node leading to processes pre-empting each other</div><div>2. Contention in your network.<br><br></div><div class="gmail_quote">On Wed, Feb 29, 2012 at 8:01 AM, Pinero, Pedro_jose <span dir="ltr">&lt;<a href="mailto:Pedro_jose.Pinero@atmel.com">Pedro_jose.Pinero@atmel.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br>

